{"tid":1534984,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"機場廁所的警暴 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T07:50:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88fc7607d134fa8727a727c5b9763f38377985e4","tid":1534984,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190903/20760722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20760722&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=160c6c99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20760722&h=e572d1c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190903/20760722</a><br />\n<br />\n機場廁所的警暴 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190903/large/1567408017_b5b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567408017_b5b1.jpg&h=9f4d85bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHKFP視頻截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.1香港國際機場洗手間，有手持警棍的躁狂警直闖入內，用力拍打各廁格的門，一見穿黑衣人就打，數人無辜被打倒地。女廁亦有肥壯女保安逐格搜查，男警大聲喝罵，黑衣少女據理力爭，叫他冷靜，眼看就要動粗，一個女生嚇得哭起來，她說丟了手機同伴來尋找&hellip;&hellip;中外媒體鏡頭下躁狂警展露獸性，實在難看，同僚拍他肩膊着他離去。<br />\n<br />\n這幕男女廁中無差別發爛渣雖比不上8.31太子站中對市民恐怖襲擊，血流滿地重傷者眾還哭作一團，但在機場上廁所人權也剝奪還遇襲？把外國記者和遊客也嚇壞了，旁觀的香港人出聲斥責，險些也遭棍擊，見到的已這樣，沒見到的何等慘烈！<br />\n<br />\n這是什麼世界？只有黑警槍杆子是她最後依靠的林鄭，才姑息養奸，視若無睹。人道危機，起碼有一半的黑警得上國際法庭受審。<br />\n<br />\n危難中的香港人，面對城破巢傾，寧鳴而死，不默而生。<br />\n<br />\n我們感謝不畏強權強暴的抗爭者守護香港，付出慘痛代價，也感謝風雨和催淚煙中的良心記者、前線救援人員（當見片段中哀求黑警讓他進地鐵站救人，甘受毆打或彈射的急救員，他痛哭，我也流淚了）&hellip;&hellip;大家本着良知保護頭爆骨斷的年輕人，直至最後一秒──這才是引以為榮的「香港人」！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n菩薩畏因，眾生畏果 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n政治害的 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"6670aeef7ab74c9bfbb7dce2d95060c16ee9c8a4","tid":1534984,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc64ad5e83e116378a939b3d2b3c6953ea37e97e","tid":1534984,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a3c62d377b19c91914ddf1addf9e4a7a18a49b6","tid":1534984,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"因為冇後果, 重有ot"},{"pid":"78c2e2b8099bd02463b864850431e9d00f834ff2","tid":1534984,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:50:45.000Z","msg":"香港人養咗班畜牲"}]}